'''''457''''' was the designation for a group of three [[CR90 corvette/Legends|CR90 corvettes]] that belonged to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. The [[Warship/Legends|warships]] had been stationed near [[Vergesso Base]] during the [[Battle of the Bajic Shipyards|Second Battle of Bajic]]; as a result of the action, all three vessels were destroyed.

